{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>About This Game</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Sect Leader\u2019s Decree</i> is a turn-based colony builder focused on resource and time management. Construct buildings, research technologies, gather resources, and train your disciples to guide your sect to prosperity!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Build and Expand</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Construct and upgrade a range of buildings, from dormitories to research labs. Each building plays a crucial role in enhancing your sect\u2019s growth and unlocking new possibilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438530/extras/buildings_gif_crop.gif?t=1738438549\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Research Technologies</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock new technologies to improve efficiency, learn new building upgrades, and discover new resources. Each completed research brings your sect closer to prosperity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438530/extras/tech_gif_final.gif?t=1738438549\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Resource Management\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manage a variety of resources, from food to building materials. Keep in mind that resources decay over time, so plan wisely not to waste them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438530/extras/resources_final.gif?t=1738438549\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Feed Your Disciples</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ensure your disciples don\u2019t go hungry! Balanced nutrition is key to maintaining their health and productivity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438530/extras/recipes_final.gif?t=1738438549\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Random Events</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face random events that can either challenge or benefit your sect. Adapt your strategies to weather natural disasters or seize unexpected opportunities. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438530/extras/events_resized.gif?t=1738438549\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your journey as a sect leader has just begun. Build a strong, prosperous sect, guide your disciples wisely, and cultivate a legacy that will be remembered for generations.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438530/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738438549","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438530/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738438549","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438530/9d70ab782132518e3c4147b47baf1717c0faf51a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738438549","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438530/9d70ab782132518e3c4147b47baf1717c0faf51a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738438549","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>About This Game</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Sect Leader\u2019s Decree</i> is a turn-based colony builder focused on resource and time management. Construct buildings, research technologies, gather resources, and train your disciples to guide your sect to prosperity!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Build and Expand</strong></p><p class=\"bb_p